{"tid":426321,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方：軒歷基斯回歸拜仁","createTime":"2017-10-06T13:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T18:16:11.000Z","uid":64181,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"2db0410c8ba53ffbbfbc5d02d3fe5137352a66ce","tid":426321,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"OFFICIAL: Jupp Heynckes returns to Bayern Munich<br />\nIt is official: Jupp Heynckes is returning to Bayern Munich as head coach.<br />\n<br />\nJust over a week after Carlo Ancelotti was sacked, the 72-year-old has agreed to take over until the end of the season.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;It isn&rsquo;t a comeback but a duty of frienship,&rdquo; Heynckes has said to German magazine kicker.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I&rsquo;ve only done it because I a owe lot to Bayern.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I have a great feeling and we can get going immediately.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nIt will be the fourth time Heynckes is Bayern manager, following two permanent spells (1987-1992 and 2011-2013) and an interim role (2009).<br />\n<br />\nLast time around, Heynckes bowed out in 2013 after winning an historic treble &ndash; still the only time it has been achieved in the club&rsquo;s illustrious history."},{"pid":"6f0bc805a1c65369dba8436c7f929309322e4003","tid":426321,"uid":64181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/213923_bf38fbbfe17108a036f3115a76490819.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F213923_bf38fbbfe17108a036f3115a76490819.jpeg&h=0da0b74c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2993211e66a54ab4ad059646ab52b42f9d1f6bf","tid":426321,"uid":64181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"72歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7e7fba908bd10fb965f570935af859295b2788","tid":42